# TGF ground-truth for the resolver golden test.
#
# Hand-authored to match `mvn dependency:tree -DoutputType=tgf -Dscope=compile`
# on jackson-databind:2.18.0 walked from a synthetic root.
#
# This is the *meaningful* transitive case: jackson-databind declares two
# compile-scope deps (jackson-annotations + jackson-core), both of which
# resolve at depth 2.  Their own transitives stop here:
# - jackson-annotations: no compile-scope deps.
# - jackson-core: parent POM unresolved in the corpus, so transitive
#   expansion halts.  In the upstream POM jackson-core itself declares
#   no compile-scope transitive deps either, so the resulting graph
#   matches Maven's output.
#
# Format: `<id> <group>:<artifact>:<version>:<scope>` per node.
1 com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-databind:2.18.0:compile
2 com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-annotations:2.18.0:compile
3 com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-core:2.18.0:compile
#
1 2 compile
1 3 compile
